Knowledge Center
Information Management

UBA Ghana will deploy “U – Direct” the Bank’s Internet Banking solution to deliver detailed on-line reports on the client's account. Security protocols and procedures will be established to ensure that information is only available to duly authorised officers of the company.

UBA Ghana will provide daily, weekly and monthly bank statements by e'mail to the client.

Advantage

  • Real-time on-line access to account details facilitates bookkeeping, minimises reconciliation errors and reduces man hours for deployment to value adding activities.
